ation meant for floating point exponents. Since the exponent here is integral (`==2`), this instance of `pow` should be replaced with a multiply. 

Existing code is:

```c
      for (i = 0; i < count; i++) {
        std += pow(mean - data_buffer[i], 2);
      }
```

Better performant code would be:

```c
      for (i = 0; i < count; i++) {
        const double dx = mean - data_buffer[i];
        std += dx * dx;
      }
```
